al directly.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the logical next step to validate the COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY hypothesis. The pulse logs exist and contain the data needed to test invariant/variant classification and next-pulse prediction.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `scripts/tic-classifier.ps1` - a PowerShell script that reads pulse logs, classifies content as invariant vs variant, and attempts to predict next pulse content from invariants. This directly implements the Phase 1 advancement experiment.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n\n[72 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774355578950}}
